OL,3,CFootballer suffers 'life-changing'
OL,4,Cinjury after post-match attack
OL,6,FA footballer has suffered a 'life-
OL,7,Fchanging injury' after being
OL,8,F'violently attacked' following a match
OL,9,Fin Cardiff on Saturday 12 October.
OL,11,FJoel Collins, 32, of Avenue Hotspur
OL,12,FFootball Club had his knee broken
OL,13,Fafter the side's away game against
OL,14,FLlanrumney Athletic Football Club.
OL,16,FThe incident is said to have involved
OL,17,Fa group of individuals who had their
OL,18,Ffaces covered and carried weapons.
