OL,6,FSouth Wales Police said it is
OL,7,Fcontinuing to investigate the attack,
OL,8,Fwhich happened at around 4pm on
OL,9,FSaturday outside Eastern Leisure
OL,10,FCentre on Llanrumney Avenue.
OL,12,FMr Collins' club has issued a
OL,13,Fstatement on social media condemning
OL,14,Fthe attack, saying it is working with
OL,15,Fthe relevant authorities to bring
OL,16,Fthose involved to justice.
