OL,3,CFootballer suffers 'life-changing'
OL,4,Cinjury after post-match attack
OL,6,FThe statement read: "This shocking
OL,7,Fincident, in which several players
OL,8,Fwere violently attacked as they left
OL,9,Fthe changing rooms, is completely
OL,10,Funacceptable and was a really
OL,11,Fdistressing and frightening experience
OL,12,Ffor everyone involved."
OL,14,FThe club added: "As a family-focused
OL,15,Fcommunity football club proud to
OL,16,Frepresent the Ely community, we are
OL,17,Fcommitted to providing a fun filled,
OL,18,Fsafe and inclusive environment for all
OL,19,Fand are hoping to return to playing in
OL,20,Fthe next few weeks."
