OL,4,Cinjury after post-match attack
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the home side for
OL,7,FSaturday's game, Llanrumney Athletic
OL,8,FFootball Club, have also issued a
OL,9,Fstatement saying they too condemn the
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FOn their X page they said: "To the
OL,13,Fclub's knowledge, no players or
OL,14,Fcoaching staff were involved in this
OL,15,Fincident and should any information
OL,16,Fcome to light to contradict this they
OL,17,Fwill be dealt with accordingly."
