OL,6,FDetective Inspector Daniel Todd of
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police said: "The level of
OL,8,Fviolence was appalling and will not be
OL,9,Ftolerated.
OL,11,F"This incident has understandably
OL,12,Fshocked the community, and it must
OL,13,Fhave been very frightening for all
OL,14,Finvolved.
OL,16,F"We are grateful for information
OL,17,Freceived so far and would appeal for
OL,18,Fany witnesses to please come forward."
